# Volunteering vocabulary

## Namespaces
### Ontology Base URI
prefix :                <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>

### Core W3C ontologies (OWL 2 reserved vocabulary)
prefix rdf:             <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
prefix rdfs:            <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
prefix owl:             <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
prefix xsd:             <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

### Other namespaces used
prefix dc:              <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
prefix skos:            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
prefix time:            <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
prefix vcard:           <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>
prefix vann:            <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>


# Class
:CharityRegistration
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "Charity Registration"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "A charity registration describes an volunteer involving organisation relationship with charity registration authorities."@en ;
    dc:description "Charity Registration"@en ;
.

# Object Properties
:charityRegistrationOrganisation
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :Registrar ;
    owl:inverseOf :organisationCharityRegistration ;
    rdfs:domain :CharityRegistration ;
    rdfs:range :Organisation ;
    rdfs:label "charity registration has organisation"@en ;
.

# Datatype Properties
:charityRegistrationRegistrar
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :registrar ;
    rdfs:domain :CharityRegistration ;
    rdfs:label "charity registration has registrar"@en ;
.

:charityRegistrationRegistrationNumber
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :registrationNumber ;
    rdfs:domain :CharityRegistration ;
    rdfs:label "charity registration has registration number"@en ;
.
